Created by Ashwin Menon

This script will send an email to your inbox when a new notice is put up on PU.

To add your email to the list, ask me (or you can set it up with the files provided here).

To get an SMS, follow the steps on this link:
http://techawakening.org/free-sms-alerts-new-email-on-gmail-with-google-docs/1130

For the filter, filter emails from: hunterofthegrove@gmail.com
and apply label sendsms

For the script (copy paste gappscript.txt from this repo), which is a modified version of the script used by default.

Feel free to improve the code.
